        <https://www.gov.uk/government/people/philip-hammond> ;
    govuk:responsibility "Defence budget"@en,
        "Defence strategy, planning, programme, and resource allocation"@en,
        "Euro-Atlantic strategy and planning"@en,
        "Independent Afghan Inquiry"@en,
        "One Defence Reform Programme"@en,
        "Service Personnel deaths on duty and letters of condolence"@en,
        "nuclear deterrent (CASD) and operations policy and enterprise"@en,
        "oversight of Veterans"@en,
        "regulatory functions"@en,
        "relationships with strategic international partners: US , France, Germany, Australia, Ukraine"@en,
        "strategic multilateral programmes – AUKUS and GCAP"@en,
        "strategic overview of the Strategic Defence Review Implementation and Defence Investment Plan"@en,
        "strategic policy and operational oversight including as a member of the National Security Council"@en ;
    govuk:roleHolder <https://www.gov.uk/government/people/john-healey> .

